data.description:
Easy one level living! Private & breezy, well maintained 3 bedroom / 2 bath home in the Town of Marshall, where lots of cool new happenings just a skip away.  This solid brick home is situated on a knoll that looks out of mountains all year long.  Room to expand in full basement with rec room & full bath, currently used as workout & shop space. A paved drive leads you up, to garage or covered metal parking cover. Porches on front, back and side great for entertaining and to take in the ever changing sky colors & stars ! 
Come visit today! 


360 Tour & Floorplan
https://youriguide.com/65_chris_nix_rdg_marshall_nc/
